    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="letter">
                <div type="text">
                    <opener>
                        <placeName>Hitcham Hadleigh Suffolk</placeName>
                        <date>27 March 1848</date>
                        <salute>Dear Sir Jn. H.</salute>
                    </opener>
                    <div type="transcription">
                        <p>I send the enclosed, as I have recommended attention to your "Discourse" - but you will observe, (if you trouble yourself to read it) that it is addressed chiefly to Mechanics, &amp; that I am without pretensions to make it worthy the attention of the well informed &amp; scientific. Airy has been giving these 6 popular lectures on Astronomy which have excited the greatest possible interest &amp; attention.</p>
                        <p>Yrs very sincerely</p>
                        <p>J. S. Henslow</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </body>
